CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 10, 1945, pg. 1, reads: "Director - Miss Suzanne La Seur is director of the People's Forum of the Irene Kaufmann Settlement. She will lead a discussion of the Refuse Collection problem at the Settlement, on Tuesday, Feb. 13. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Suzanne Le Seur, director of People's Forum at Irene Kaufmann Settlement, posed in office
